ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of ROBYN SNEATH of Brandon, Manitoba, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum for Human Rights, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective June 22, 2019, in the place of Jeannette F. Acheson, whose term will expired.
